# Terminology snapshot

**Full ordlista:** [`docs/architecture/glossary.md`](../../docs/architecture/glossary.md). **Målbild:** [`docs/architecture/llm-flow-target-worldclass.md`](../../docs/architecture/llm-flow-target-worldclass.md). **Signal-ägarmatris:** [`docs/architecture/llm-signal-flow.md`](../../docs/architecture/llm-signal-flow.md).

**Grundregel:** kod är source of truth. Ny term bara om befintlig inte räcker — kolla glossaryn först. Konsolidera hellre än ny jargong.

## Signal-gate

Innan du lägger till en signal/ordlista/keyword-array: (1) finns canonical source redan? → ändra **ägaren**, inte konsumenten. (2) Ny signal → registrera i ägarmatrisen.

| Signal | Canonical source |
|--------|-----------------|
| Domän / site-type | `config/domain-rules.json` → `domain-inference.ts` |
| Prompt-heuristik | `config/prompt-heuristic-tokens.json` → `prompt-heuristics.ts` |
| Init-semantik | Deep Brief (`site-brief-generation.ts`) |
| Follow-up-semantik | Snapshot-brief (`buildFollowUpBriefFromSnapshot`) — aldrig ny full Deep Brief |
| Designregler | Core Rules (`config/prompt-core/`) + `buildDynamicContext` |
| Build intent | `BUILD_INTENT_GUIDANCE` i `intent-guidance.ts` |
| Capability → dossier-bridge | `orchestrate.ts` `inferredCapabilityIds` |

## Förväxlingstabell (skriv höger kolumn, undvik vänster)

| Säg | Inte |
|-----|------|
| `own-engine` | generatorn, v0-motorn |
| `preview` / `VM` / `preview_host` | sandbox (utom legacy) |
| `template-library` | "mallar" om du menar katalogen |
| `scaffolds` | mallar/templates (om runtime-startpunkter) |
| `scaffold variant` | scaffold family, style direction (borttaget) |
| `Deep Brief` (init) / `Snapshot-Brief` (follow-up) | brief, StructuredBrief, PromptAssist-paraply |
| **mekanisk autofix** / **LLM-fix** | "autofix" blandat ihop |
| `previewUrl` | demoUrl (legacy) |
| `backoffice/` | "dashboard" (legacy) |
| `Core Rules` | "prompt-static" (legacy) |
| F2 (`fidelity2`) / F3 (`fidelity3`) | "tier 2" / "tier 3" (utom om du pratar om quality-gate-lanes) |

## Tre meningar för fas-skillnaden

- **Init** = bygg ny artifact graph (genesis). Full Deep Brief, scaffold-pick, dossier-pick, route-plan från scratch.
- **Follow-up** = delta-operation på existerande graph. Snapshot-brief, fryst scaffold/variant, frysta routes (utom `clear-redesign`).
- **F2 vs F3** = `previewPolicy: fidelity2` (design-loop, default) vs `fidelity3` (integrationer, explicit "Bygg integrationer"-knapp). F3-versioner pekar på sin F2-fork via `parent_version_id`.

## `v0` betyder tre saker

(1) `/api/v0/` API-versionering · (2) naming debt i symboler · (3) Mallar-tab. `v0-sdk`, `src/lib/v0/`, `V0_API_KEY` borta ur runtime.
